, \"from\": 1251, \"to\": 1269}, {\"ngram\": \"the moon\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1292}, {\"ngram\": \"her success\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am so happy I finally got my gold medal.\\\"\", \"from\": 1410, \"to\": 1453, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my gold medal\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1451}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Hodgkinson, from Atherton,Greater Manchester, has been dreaming of gold since the Tokyo Games where she claimed silver.\", \"from\": 1455, \"to\": 1574, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1455, \"end\": 1465, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.996162264266641, \"rank\": 0.003852520689475186, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 1472, \"end\": 1480, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Atherton\", \"score\": 0.9999899084054847, \"rank\": 1.009169604995421e-05, \"text\": \"Atherton\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Atherton\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Atherton\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Greater Manchester\", \"from\": 1481, \"to\": 1499}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1522, \"to\": 1526}, {\"ngram\": \"the Tokyo Games\", \"from\": 1533, \"to\": 1548}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1573}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She said: \\\"I think it was always an aim by Paris to try and be in a position to upgrade that to gold, and after so many silver medals in a global stage in my sport\\u2026 this one really meant the most and there is no better place to do it than theOlympicsto upgrade.\\\"\", \"from\": 1576, \"to\": 1838, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1619, \"end\": 1624, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997612576, \"rank\": 2.389470994412807e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an aim\", \"from\": 1609, \"to\": 1615}, {\"ngram\": \"a position\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1652}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 1672, \"to\": 1676}, {\"ngram\": \"so many silver medals\", \"from\": 1688, \"to\": 1709}, {\"ngram\": \"a global stage\", \"from\": 1713, \"to\": 1727}, {\"ngram\": \"my sport\", \"from\": 1731, \"to\": 1739}, {\"ngram\": \"this one\", \"from\": 1741, \"to\": 1749}, {\"ngram\": \"no better place\", \"from\": 1785, \"to\": 1800}, {\"ngram\": \"theOlympicsto upgrade\", \"from\": 1815, \"to\": 1836}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The athlete did not balk when asked if she was aiming for domination in the field, saying: \\\"Why not?\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1940, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The athlete\", \"from\": 1840, \"to\": 1851}, {\"ngram\": \"domination\", \"from\": 1898, \"to\": 1908}, {\"ngram\": \"the field\", \"from\": 1912, \"to\": 1921}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Why not aim high, see what else is out there?\", \"from\": 1941, \"to\": 1986, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I still do not have a world championship gold, so there is still plenty more to be done.\\\"\", \"from\": 1987, \"to\": 2076, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a world championship gold\", \"from\": 2007, \"to\": 2032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On potentially becoming a poster girl for the sport, Hodgkinson told PA: \\\"I think that's such a privileged position to be in.\", \"from\": 2078, \"to\": 2203, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2131, \"end\": 2141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.996162264266641, \"rank\": 0.003852520689475186, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a poster girl\", \"from\": 2102, \"to\": 2115}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 2120, \"to\": 2129}, {\"ngram\": \"PA\", \"from\": 2147, \"to\": 2149}, {\"ngram\": \"such a privileged position\", \"from\": 2167, \"to\": 2193}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I'd love for people to see me that way, it's such an honour.\\\"\", \"from\": 2204, \"to\": 2265, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"people\", \"from\": 2217, \"to\": 2223}, {\"ngram\": \"such an honour\", \"from\": 2249, \"to\": 2263}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Her strength and conditioning coach Dane Mitchell said Hodgkinson was made for the added attention that will come her way after her gold medal, insisting she is a \\\"superstar\\\".\", \"from\": 2267, \"to\": 2442, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2308, \"end\": 2316, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitchell_family\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.429220641991148e-12, \"text\": \"Mitchell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitchell_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitchell_family\"}, {\"begin\": 2322, \"end\": 2332, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.996162264266641, \"rank\": 0.003852520689475186, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the added attention\", \"from\": 2346, \"to\": 2365}, {\"ngram\": \"her gold medal\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2409}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"superstar\", \"from\": 2428, \"to\": 2440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Mr Mitchell, who has worked with Hodgkinson for around five years, watched the race on TV from home and was \\\"pretty gutted\\\" not to be in Paris.\", \"from\": 2444, \"to\": 2587, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2447, \"end\": 2455, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitchell_family\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.429220641991148e-12, \"text\": \"Mitchell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitchell_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitchell_family\"}, {\"begin\": 2477, \"end\": 2487, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.996162264266641, \"rank\": 0.003852520689475186, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 2581, \"end\": 2586, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999997612576, \"rank\": 2.389470994412807e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"around five years\", \"from\": 2492, \"to\": 2509}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 2519, \"to\": 2527}, {\"ngram\": \"TV\", \"from\": 2531, \"to\": 2533}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 2539, \"to\": 2543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The head of strength and conditioning at Leeds Beckett University told PA: \\\"(I am) absolutely over the moon for her, really.\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2713, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2630, \"end\": 2654, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds_Beckett_University\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Leeds Beckett University\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds_Beckett_University\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Leeds_Beckett_University\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The head\", \"from\": 2589, \"to\": 2597}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 2601, \"to\": 2609}, {\"ngram\": \"conditioning\", \"from\": 2614, \"to\": 2626}, {\"ngram\": \"PA\", \"from\": 2660, \"to\": 2662}, {\"ngram\": \"the moon\", \"from\": 2688, \"to\": 2696}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So, so proud of her.\\\"\", \"from\": 2714, \"to\": 2735, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said one of his first reactions after her race was relief because there had been \\\"so much pressure\\\" for her.\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2848, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his first reactions\", \"from\": 2752, \"to\": 2771}, {\"ngram\": \"her race\", \"from\": 2778, \"to\": 2786}, {\"ngram\": \"relief\", \"from\": 2791, \"to\": 2797}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"so much pressure\", \"from\": 2821, \"to\": 2838}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I did know, deepest, deep down, I knew that if there was anyone who could cope with the pressure and rise to those big occasions, it is Keely,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 2850, \"to\": 3007, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"anyone\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2918}, {\"ngram\": \"the pressure\", \"from\": 2939, \"to\": 2951}, {\"ngram\": \"those big occasions\", \"from\": 2964, \"to\": 2983}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I knew she would do it, but it's just brilliant to actually do it, you know, it's on paper: Olympic champion.\", \"from\": 3009, \"to\": 3119, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"paper\", \"from\": 3095, \"to\": 3100}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympic champion\", \"from\": 3102, \"to\": 3118}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It's still sinking in, it's incredible.\\\"\", \"from\": 3120, \"to\": 3160, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"He said he was \\\"sweating\\\" and out of his seat shouting at his TV during the race.\", \"from\": 3162, \"to\": 3243, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his seat\", \"from\": 3199, \"to\": 3207}, {\"ngram\": \"his TV\", \"from\": 3220, \"to\": 3226}, {\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3234, \"to\": 3242}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just really was hoping she executed what she's capable of and she did,\\\" Mr Mitchell said.\", \"from\": 3245, \"to\": 3337, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3323, \"end\": 3331, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitchell_family\", \"score\": 0.999999999992724, \"rank\": 7.429220641991148e-12, \"text\": \"Mitchell\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitchell_family\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mitchell_family\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She really controlled the race.\", \"from\": 3339, \"to\": 3371, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the race\", \"from\": 3362, \"to\": 3370}]}, {\"sentence\": \"It was a masterclass, really, in tactical racing.\", \"from\": 3372, \"to\": 3421, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a masterclass\", \"from\": 3379, \"to\": 3392}, {\"ngram\": \"tactical racing\", \"from\": 3405, \"to\": 3420}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I was just so pleased when she crossed that line, and just to see her face, I nearly welled up, to be honest.\\\"\", \"from\": 3423, \"to\": 3534, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"that line\", \"from\": 3463, \"to\": 3472}, {\"ngram\": \"her face\", \"from\": 3490, \"to\": 3498}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The coach spoke a few weeks ago with Hodgkinson's father Dean, who told him: \\\"We think it's her time this time round,\\\" and Mr Mitchell said he felt the same.\", \"from\": 3536, \"to\": 3693, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3573, \"end\": 3583, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"score\": 0.996162264266641, \"rank\": 0.003852520689475186, \"text\": \"Hodgkinson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tim_Hodgkinson\"}, {\"begin\": 3593, \"end\": 3597, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"score\": 0.999999995057351, \"rank\": 2.6268070412119135e-09, \"text\": \"Dean\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Dean_Winchester\", \"dbpe